"PCB-1016-00" appears to be silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. :The [[i-connect AP880G|'''i-connect''' AP880G]] (FCC ID: RMA000001) appears to share the same board. The test report for the AP880G's filing notes its manufacturer as [http://www.rfnetech.com/ '''RFNET Technologies Pte Ltd'''].. they are the presumed manuf. of this device (probable [[RFNet APRT-2001g]])
The sample SSID shown in the manual is '''11g'''.. and it is noted as being the default in the AP880G's FCC manual. It is presumed to indeed be '''11g'''.
The power supply noted in the test report is a '''SY''' SY-0901 (120VAC ~ 60Hz, 150mA -> 9VDC, 1.0A).
